captions.text:
-LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
THE GREAT BILL BURR. BILL BURR!

-ALL RIGHT.
THANK YOU.
WOW.

ALL RIGHT, HOW ARE YOU?
HOW'S IT GOING?

THANK YOU FOR COMING OUT
ON THIS WONDERFUL EVENING.

I JUST GOT BACK
FROM SOUTHEAST ASIA,
DOING SOME STAND-UP OVER THERE.

REALLY COOL PEOPLE.
YEAH, IT'S THE SHIT.
WONDERFUL PEOPLE.

UNBELIEVABLE LEVEL
OF POVERTY AND STUFF --
AS I ALMOST FELL OFF THE STAGE.

IT MAKES IT HARD TO COMPLAIN,
THOUGH, YOU KNOW,

WHEN YOU SEE
THAT LEVEL OF POVERTY.

YOU COME BACK, YOU'RE THROAT'S
ALL ITCHING AND STUFF.
PROBABLY GOT EBOLA, YOU KNOW?
[ CHUCKLES ]

IT WOULD BE A GREAT THING
TO BRING THAT HERE, YOU KNOW?

JUST TO KIND OF THIN OUT
THE TRAFFIC A LITTLE BIT.
RIGHT?

WHY DON'T THEY EVER JUST LET IT
BURN THROUGH ONE TIME?

WHY DO WE ALWAYS GOT TO, LIKE,
JUMP ON IT?

YOU EVER HAD ONE OF
THOSE SELFISH THOUGHTS,

LIKE, WHEN IT WAS
A BUNCH OF PEOPLE WHO DIED?
NOBODY YOU KNEW OR LOVED, RIGHT?
AND THEN, THE NEXT DAY,

YOU JUST GET TO TEAR
RIGHT THROUGH THE LINCOLN TUNNEL

AT ABOUT 5:00 IN THE EVENING,
RIGHT?

THE ONLY THING YOU'D HAVE
TO SUPPRESS

IS THE GUILT OF NOT MISSING
THOSE PEOPLE YOU DIDN'T KNOW.
RIGHT?
[ CHUCKLES ]

I SHOULDN'T MAKE FUN OF EBOLA.
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT IT.
OTHER THAN IF YOU GET IT,

YOU HAVE AN UNBELIEVABLE URGE
TO GO TO THE AIRPORT.
ALL RIGHT?
YEAH, I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT IS.

NOBODY WHO GETS EBOLA
JUST HAS THE DECENCY

TO JUST WALK OUT
IN THE WOODS BY THEMSELVES

AND JUST BLEED OUT
LIKE A GENTLEMAN, RIGHT?

FOR SOME REASON YOU GOT TO GO
RIGHT DOWN TO THE AIRPORT.

"OH, CAN I DOWNGRADE
TO A MIDDLE SEAT?"
[ COUGHING ]
SO...
I'M SICK OF OBAMA'S WIFE.
YEAH.

THIS ISN'T
SOME REPUBLICAN RANT, EITHER.

IT'S JUST KIND OF
FIRST LADIES IN GENERAL.

YOU KNOW,
I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT IS.

ALL THROUGHOUT MY LIFE,
WITH EACH PRESIDENCY,

LIKE, THESE FIRST LADIES,
THEY'VE JUST GOTTEN
MORE AND MORE, LIKE, CHATTY.
YOU KNOW?

MORE AND MORE CHIMING IN,
LIKE LEANING INTO THE FRAME,
SPITTING OUT THEIR IDEAS.

IT'S JUST LIKE,
"WELL, WHY ARE YOU TALKING?"

RIGHT?
YOU WEREN'T ELECTED.
SHUT UP.

YOU'RE HUSBAND'S NOT RUNNING
A LEMONADE STAND HERE.
HE'S RUNNING THE COUNTRY.
YOU DON'T JUST CHIME IN.

LET ME GUESS --
IS THIS CONSIDERED SEXIST?
IT IS? WHY?

OKAY, YOU JUST NODDED, THERE,
LADY.
LET ME ASK YOU THIS, ALL RIGHT?

LET'S SAY YOU HAD
A LEAK IN YOUR HOUSE, OKAY?

YOU CALL THE PLUMBER UP.
HE SHOWS UP.

AND HE GOES,
"YEAH, I THINK THE LEAK'S COMING
FROM THE YOU UPSTAIRS BATHROOM.

WE NEED TO SHUT IT OFF,"
BAH-BAH-BAH.

THEN, ALL OF A SUDDEN
HIS WIFE WALKS IN,
WHO ISN'T A PLUMBER

AND THEN GOES, "OH, YOU KNOW,
I ACTUALLY THINK IT'S KIND OF"
[ MUTTERING ]

WOULD YOU BE LIKE,
"WITH ALL DUE RESPECT,
SHUT THE FUCK UP"?
I NEED A PLUMBER IN THIS MOMENT.

I'LL EXTEND
AN OLIVE BRANCH HERE.

ALL RIGHT, AT SOME POINT,
THERE'S GONNA BE

THE FIRST FEMALE PRESIDENT,
RIGHT?

[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]
EXACTLY.
WHICH MEANS, AT THAT MOMENT,

YOU'RE GONNA HAVE THE FIRST
MALE FIRST LADY, RIGHT?
AND WHAT THAT HAPPENS,

THAT DUDE NEEDS
TO SHUT HIS TRAP.

I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
A WORD OUT OF HIM.

I WANT TO HEAR
FROM THE PRESIDENT.

YOU, SIR, GO DO SOME
FIRST-LADY STUFF, ALL RIGHT?

GET YOURSELVES SOME GLOVES
THAT GO UP TO YOUR ELBOWS.
SMILE AND NOD DURING SPEECHES.

GO PUT YOUR OWN FLAIR
REDECORATING THE WHITE HOUSE.
RIGHT?

WHICH LEADS YOU
TO MICHELLE OBAMA, RIGHT?

AND NOW SHE'S SITTING THERE
HOLDING UP THOSE HASHTAGS.

REMEMBER THAT HASHTAG
#BringBackOurGirls?

REMEMBER THAT? IT'S LIKE --
IT BLEW MY MIND.

IT'S LIKE,
"WHY ARE YOU SHOWING ME THAT?"
I'M A STAND-UP COMEDIAN.

LIKE, WHAT AM I GONNA DO
TO GET THOSE GIRLS BACK?

WHY DON'T YOU LOOK
ACROSS THE DINNER TABLE?"
IT'S LIKE, "YOU SEE THAT GUY?

THAT IS
THE LEADER OF THE FREE WORLD.
TELL HIM TO PICK UP THE PHONE,

CALL SOME NAVY SEALS,
AND SOLVE IT."
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

SHOW UP
WITH A SHARPENED MIKE STAND?

"YEAH, MICHELLE SAID
TO BRING THEM BACK!"
OH, IT'S UNREAL.
[ CHUCKLES ]

I'LL TELL YOU WHAT KILLS ME --
HILLARY CLINTON MIGHT RUN.

SHE MIGHT RUN.
THAT BLOWS MY --

I DON'T EVEN KNOW
HOW SHE BECAME A SENATOR.

SHE WENT FROM BEING
THE PRESIDENT'S WIFE

TO BEING A SENATOR
JUST LIKE THAT -- LATERAL MOVE.

THAT'S LIKE
TOM BRADY'S WIFE BECOMING

THE NEXT QUARTERBACK
OF THE RAMS.

IT'S LIKE,
"WHAT, YOU'RE HANGING OUT?
YOU JUST PICK IT UP?"
"I SUCKED AT SPORTS,

AND THEN I BANGED TOM BRADY,
AND I DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED!

I JUST PICKED UP THE BALL.
I STARTED LACING IT.

I'M LEADING RECEIVERS.
IT WAS INCREDIBLE."
[ CHUCKLES ]

"I KNEW IT WAS GONNA BE
LIKE THIS."
YOU KNOW WHAT'S FUNNY?

THERE'S ACTUALLY
PEOPLE OUT THERE

THAT THINK
A WOMAN BEING PRESIDENT

IS ACTUALLY A GOOD IDEA,
YOU KNOW?
CAN YOU BELIEVE IN A THAT?
SEE THAT? THEY DO.

"THAT'LL DO SOMETHING.
THAT'LL CHANGE THINGS."
HOW?

HOW THE FUCK IS THAT GONNA
CHANGE ANYTHING?

DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THE PRESIDENT MAKES A YEAR?

THE PRESIDENT MAKES
400 GRAND A YEAR.
THAT'S IT.

HE'S TRYING TO KEEP BILLIONAIRES
IN LINE MAKING 400 GRAND A YEAR.
THAT'S ALL HE MAKES.

HE MAKES THAN SOME PEOPLE
BLOGGING ON THE INTERNET.

THE PRESIDENT SHOULD HAVE
"FUCK YOU" MONEY, ALL RIGHT?

HE SHOULDN'T BE THERE WITH HIS
POCKETS TURNED OUT SAYING,

"I NEED YOUR HELP
TO GET ME THE JOB."
RIGHT?

WHAT, DO YOU GUYS ALL DONATE
TO THE CAMPAIGN?
IS THAT WHAT IT IS?
THE BAND'S ENJOYING IT.
MARTHA STEWART, NOT SO MUCH,

BUT THE REST OF YOU --
ENJOYING IT.
THEY'RE JUST JOKES, MARTHA.

COME ON, YOU GOT AN EMPIRE.
I'M ROOTING FOR YOU.
ALL RIGHT, I'M OUT OF TIME.

YOU GUYS WERE AWESOME.
THANK YOU SO MUCH.
